descp2: Controls the shape of the returned op's output. If`True`, the returned op will produce a 3-D tensor for PNG, JPEG, and BMP files; and a 4-D tensor for all GIFs, whether animated or not. If,`False`, the returned op will produce a 3-D tensor for all file types and will truncate animated GIFs to the first frame.
